titleNullable: Nike & Yeezy's DATASET (Third week of Jan 2018)
subtitleNullable: Sneaker Sale & Resale Dataset for Nike & Yeezy's on StockX
descriptionNullable: This dataset is a cleaner and smaller version of the StockX.com sneaker sales dataset. The dataset has all the retail and resale prices of Nike and Yeezy's Sneakers on the StockX website from 2017 to 2019. I personally wanted to use the dataset for my college assignment, so I reduced the data to only one week from January 2018 as well as removed all the duplicate data values.
